cac:ProcurementProject.cbc:Name: Dynamic Purchasing System for Training Services for Tech Northwest Skillnet, on behalf of Atlantic Technological University
cac:ProcurementProject.cbc:Description: Tech Northwest Skillnet on behalf of Atlantic Technological University wishes to establish a Dynamic Purchasing System (DPS) under eight (8) lots for Training Services. The focus is on Training for ICT and Technology Companies (LOT 1) but will also cover General Business Training under Lots 2-8. Most of the training will take place in person in Donegal, Sligo or Leitrim. On occasion there will be a request for an online course to be delivered. Most programmes are delivered for groups of 10-15 people. These may be employees from some of the large Fintech/ICT employers in the region. They may also be made up on Owners/Managers of SMEs in the region. In general, the training provider will be asked to provide a Tutor, Venue with relevant facilities, Course Material, Refreshments and Accreditation in some circumstances.

efac:SelectionCriteria.cbc:Name: Economic and financial standing, and Technical and Professional ability.
